GSD.description:
f2fs: fix to do sanity check on destination blkaddr during recovery

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.150 by commit 73fb4bd2c055a393816f078f158cdd3025006f1d. For more details please see the references link.
